Changelog
==========

0.23
-----

* Add hooks to record cost of test_connection/produce_client.
* Catch socket.error when connection abruptly terminated.
* Better exception handling for call hooks.


0.22
-----

* Add tornado support.
* Use deque instead of set to store connections in pool.


0.15
-----

* Add full hook support.
* Python3 optimizations to imports and threading.
* Can set temporary timeout for client.
